<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.2">
<l>kaṭaliṟ piṟantu karutātu pañcacaṉa</l>
<l>ṉuṭalil vaḷarntupō yūḻiyāṉ kaittalat</l>
<l>tiṭariṟ kuṭiyēṟit tīya vacurar</l>
<l>naṭalaip paṭamuḻaṅkun tōṟṟattāy naṟcaṅkē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O good conch! You have the power to thunder</l>
<l>so that the evil Asuras suffer distress,</l>
<l>being born in the sea, growing up in the body of Pañcajana,</l>
<l>not minding [either and] settling in the elevated [spot]</l>
<l rend="indent">that is the palm of the ancient God.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
